data.description: This unique 2 bedroom 2.5 bath townhome with basement has so much potential to expand and is located in the great city of Smyrna!! Only one other attached unit makes this townhome feel more like a detached single family home with big, private backyard! Convenient to the East-West connector, Braves stadium, shopping, restaurants, Silver Comet Trail, parks and major expressways, I-75 and I-285! The main level features a cozy kitchen with breakfast area and bayed window, stainless steel appliances, white cabinets and open view to the dining room/family room. An updated powder room, dining area with bayed window, and family room with brick fireplace and access to huge deck off the back completes the main level. Upstairs the master bedroom features a walk in closet and private updated bath with walk in shower with gorgeous tiles. The secondary guest bedroom also features a walk in closet and updated private bathroom with soaking tub and bayed window. The basement offers so much potential to expand! There is an open family room/media room that has been completely finished with tile floors. An additional bedroom and storage hall have been finished with dry wall and painted. Just install your flooring and baseboards and you can move right in! The basement has access to the huge partially fenced backyard where there is so much space to entertain! This special community truly feels more like detached homes than townhomes. If you are looking for townhome space with the privacy and backyard of a detached home, you have found your match! Freshly painted through out, this home just awaits your finishing touches. Level driveway and level walk-in entry make this the perfect place to call home. An amazing deal for under $300,000 in sought after Smyrna location!
